ZH: 我们千万不能错过这场音乐会。
EN: We must not miss this concert at all costs.

ZH: 我千万不会相信他说的话。
EN: I will never believe what he says no matter what.

ZH: 千万不能忘记带伞，天气很不稳定。
EN: Don't forget to bring an umbrella at all costs, the weather is very unpredictable.

ZH: 千万不要迟到，老板会生气的。
EN: Don't be late at all costs, the boss will be angry.

ZH: 今天千万不要忘记买菜。
EN: Don't forget to buy groceries today at all costs.

ZH: 千万别告诉任何人我的秘密。
EN: Do not tell anyone my secret under any circumstances.

ZH: 千万不要忘记锁门。
EN: Make sure to lock the door without fail.

ZH: 千万要注意安全，不要冒险。
EN: Make sure to prioritize safety and not take risks.

ZH: 千万不要轻易放弃，坚持下去就会成功。
EN: Never give up easily, success will come as long as you persist.

ZH: 千万要谨慎行事，不要冲动做出决定。
EN: Be cautious in your actions and do not make decisions impulsively.

ZH: 千万不要忘记查看行程，以免错过飞机。
EN: Don't forget to double check your itinerary so you don't miss your flight.

ZH: 千万别忘了向老师请教困难问题。
EN: Be sure to ask the teacher for help with difficult questions.

ZH: 千万不要太担心，一切会好起来的。
EN: Don't worry too much, everything will be fine.

ZH: 千万不要让这次失败影响你的信心。
EN: Don't let this failure affect your confidence.

ZH: 千万不要因小失大，要懂得取舍。
EN: Don't lose sight of the forest for the trees, know how to prioritize.

ZH: 千万不要被别人的成功影响到自己的进步。
EN: Don't let other people's success hinder your own progress.

ZH: 千万不要因为困难而放弃理想。
EN: Don't give up your dreams because of difficulties.

ZH: 千万不要忘记感激生活中的美好。
EN: Don't forget to appreciate the beauty in life.

ZH: 千万不能沉湎于过去的悲伤。
EN: Don't dwell on past sorrows at all costs.
